01:27:10.996 --> 01:27:15.867
And I'm sorry to say that
the world has become a pussy-whipped...

1248
01:27:16.084 --> 01:27:20.256
...Brady Bunch version of itself,
run by a bunch of robed sissies.

1249
01:27:21.299 --> 01:27:24.093
All we have to do to run the whole thing...

1250
01:27:24.218 --> 01:27:28.139
...is to kill a man named Friendly,
who put it all together.

1251
01:27:29.290 --> 01:27:31.894
Ah, but there's an extra added bonus.

1252
01:27:33.645 --> 01:27:35.147
We get to kill...

1253
01:27:35.314 --> 01:27:37.649
...the man who put most of us behind the freezer.

1254
01:27:37.816 --> 01:27:38.984
You mean...

1255
01:27:39.151 --> 01:27:40.903
...we get to kill John Spartan?

1256
01:27:40.986 --> 01:27:42.154
Exactly.

1257
01:27:42.488 --> 01:27:45.742
I want you to loot, pillage,
plunder, I want you to steal.

1258
01:27:46.076 --> 01:27:50.538
I want you to do all the wonderful things
that we used to do before any of this happened.

1259
01:27:51.289 --> 01:27:53.333
This world will be ours!

1260
01:27:53.541 --> 01:27:55.376
Let's bring back the good old days!

1261
01:27:55.460 --> 01:27:56.837
Are you with me?

1262
01:27:57.246 --> 01:27:59.673
Are you with me? Let's do it!

1263
01:28:02.510 --> 01:28:06.639
It is a curious conclusion
which you have deduced, John Spartan.

1264
01:28:07.515 --> 01:28:10.268
But I can find no fault in your logic.

1265
01:28:10.393 --> 01:28:14.523
Simon Phoenix is the perfect weapon to send
out into the savage outer regions in which we stand.

1266
01:28:15.232 --> 01:28:17.192
I'm impressed, John Spartan.

1267
01:28:17.401 --> 01:28:20.028
You mean they thawed this guy out just to kill me?

1268
01:28:21.113 --> 01:28:24.242
- I'm flattered.
- Don't be flattered. Be frightened.

1269
01:28:24.492 --> 01:28:26.702
This guy's a certifiable nightmare.

1270
01:28:26.869 --> 01:28:28.871
- And that's why you're down here?
- Yeah.

1271
01:28:31.249 --> 01:28:34.837
I must have done something right
in the previous life.

1272
01:28:35.337 --> 01:28:37.840
Can't imagine what that could have been.

1273
01:28:39.800 --> 01:28:41.510
Two for the price of one.

1274
01:28:41.760 --> 01:28:43.429
Let's take them boys.

1275
01:28:48.393 --> 01:28:49.727
Stay down!

1276
01:29:22.846 --> 01:29:25.767
I'll be goddamned.
Like a New York cockroach.

1277
01:29:55.507 --> 01:29:57.217
Everything's gone wrong.

1278
01:30:03.918 --> 01:30:05.118
Phoenix!

1279
01:30:13.735 --> 01:30:16.196
There's an elevator shaft on top of this place.

1280
01:30:18.490 --> 01:30:20.033
Does that mean we're going up?

1281
01:30:20.200 --> 01:30:22.786
Momentito, Senorita Huxley. Come on.

1282
01:30:41.432 --> 01:30:44.143
How nice! Must've been expecting me.

1283
01:31:01.077 --> 01:31:02.329
Okay, now what?

1284
01:31:02.413 --> 01:31:03.789
Buckle up.

1285
01:31:27.231 --> 01:31:29.192
There he is! He's in my car!

1286
01:31:35.239 --> 01:31:36.657
Goddamn it.

1287
01:31:43.248 --> 01:31:45.417
What's happening to cops today?

1288
01:31:45.501 --> 01:31:48.128
Don't you know you are
endangering the lives of civilians?

1289
01:32:06.774 --> 01:32:07.650
Auto-inflate!

1290
01:32:07.733 --> 01:32:09.068
"Auto-inflate"

1291
01:32:11.069 --> 01:32:12.069
Damn!

1292
01:32:14.615 --> 01:32:15.742
Oh, that's just lovely.

1293
01:32:15.826 --> 01:32:17.327
Huxley, drive!

1294
01:32:17.469 --> 01:32:20.247
Okay, okay. I've read all about this, now... okay.

1295
01:32:22.833 --> 01:32:25.127
What do I do? I just, I just push this pedal?

1296
01:32:26.128 --> 01:32:27.128
Whoa!

1297
01:32:27.546 --> 01:32:29.132
Okay, okay. I got it, I got it.

1298
01:32:38.683 --> 01:32:40.017
Punch it, Huxley!

1299
01:32:40.269 --> 01:32:41.353
Excuse me?

1300
01:32:41.478 --> 01:32:43.981
Push the pedal as hard as you can!
Just catch up to him.

1301
01:32:53.576 --> 01:32:54.576
Shit!

1302
01:32:55.277 --> 01:32:56.628
No free rides!

1303
01:33:02.375 --> 01:33:03.960
Emergency, doors open.

1304
01:33:04.043 --> 01:33:05.296
"Doors opening"

1305
01:33:06.589 --> 01:33:08.299
Say hello to my old friend.

1306
01:33:20.562 --> 01:33:21.646
Doors close!

1307
01:33:21.730 --> 01:33:22.898
"Malfunction"

1308
01:33:28.528 --> 01:33:30.406
Computer, auto-drive.

1309
01:33:30.656 --> 01:33:32.366
"Auto-drive engaged"

1310
01:33:32.533 --> 01:33:34.452
Going to give you a haircut!

1311
01:33:35.953 --> 01:33:38.122
Remember those 40 bus passengers...

1312
01:33:38.206 --> 01:33:40.625
...that you blew apart trying to catch me?

1313
01:33:42.002 --> 01:33:44.004
They were already dead.

1314
01:33:44.463 --> 01:33:46.298
Cold as Haagen-Dazs!

1315
01:33:54.390 --> 01:33:57.018
Man, I went to jail with a 36-year smile.

1316
01:33:58.228 --> 01:33:59.687
You're dead, Spartan.

1317
01:33:59.896 --> 01:34:01.689
Speak for yourself.

1318
01:34:10.908 --> 01:34:11.867
Self-drive!

1319
01:34:11.951 --> 01:34:13.702
"Unable to execute"

1320
01:34:13.994 --> 01:34:15.663
- Self-drive, now!
"Malfunction"

1321
01:34:15.746 --> 01:34:17.498
"Unable to execute"

1322
01:34:17.748 --> 01:34:18.917
Emergency!

1323
01:34:20.961 --> 01:34:22.087
Brake!

1324
01:34:23.421 --> 01:34:24.923
"Self-drive engaged"

1325
01:34:26.550 --> 01:34:28.093
Brake! Brake!

1326
01:34:30.429 --> 01:34:33.391
Brake now, you
Mickey Mouse piece of shit!

1327
01:35:06.135 --> 01:35:07.135
John Spartan?

1328
01:35:08.136 --> 01:35:09.847
John Spartan, are you in there?

1329
01:35:10.473 --> 01:35:11.473
John Spartan?

1330
01:35:11.474 --> 01:35:13.642
Who do you think it is, Huxley?

1331
01:35:21.860 --> 01:35:24.988
I thought your life force
had been prematurely terminated!

1332
01:35:25.071 --> 01:35:27.324
Yeah, I thought I was history too.

1333
01:35:27.491 --> 01:35:31.244
What the hell happened? All the sudden,
this car turned into a cannoli.

1334
01:35:31.495 --> 01:35:34.290
It's secur-a-foam. It saved your life.

1335
01:35:34.499 --> 01:35:36.834
Look at you, you're in shambles.

1336
01:35:37.126 --> 01:35:40.505
Don't worry, I can fix it later.
All I need is a needle and thread.

1337
01:35:40.838 --> 01:35:42.757
I really didn't say that, did I?

1338
01:35:42.858 --> 01:35:43.958
Damn!

1339
01:35:50.684 --> 01:35:55.187
John Spartan, you... You caveman, you're under arrest!

1340
01:35:55.771 --> 01:35:58.358
You're to be returned to the cryo-prison.
Immediately!

1341
01:35:58.441 --> 01:36:01.152
I heard all about that. We'll talk later, Chief.

1342
01:36:01.703 --> 01:36:04.181
Right now, I need something, anything. A shotgun, a flare gun.

1343
01:36:04.182 --> 01:36:05.282
- Spartan.
- What?

1344
01:36:08.868 --> 01:36:09.744
Shit!

1345
01:36:09.912 --> 01:36:11.413
Defensive red alert!

1346
01:36:13.124 --> 01:36:14.542
Stun batons on.

1347
01:36:15.876 --> 01:36:17.086
Relax.

1348
01:36:18.045 --> 01:36:19.880
Well, look at you, you get a bump on the noggin...

1349
01:36:19.964 --> 01:36:22.133
...and you think you're Pancho Villa?

1350
01:36:22.634 --> 01:36:23.593
Who?

1351
01:36:24.094 --> 01:36:24.970
Never mind.

1352
01:36:25.053 --> 01:36:26.596
Time to take a stand, pal.

1353
01:36:26.680 --> 01:36:30.308
Well, good. While you're doing it,
loan me a gun. Loan me two guns.

1354
01:36:30.559 --> 01:36:34.480
You'd use these weapons of mass destruction
against men and women who uphold the law?

1355
01:36:34.689 --> 01:36:37.567
We use these weapons
to shop for groceries, dick.

1356
01:36:37.734 --> 01:36:39.734
Spartan, wait!

1357
01:36:39.735 --> 01:36:41.112
You can't leave.

1358
01:36:41.320 --> 01:36:46.033
You're under arrest. This very concept
negates the possibility of your leaving.

1359
01:36:46.242 --> 01:36:47.828
Skip it, Chief.

1360
01:36:48.287 --> 01:36:50.038
Lieutenant Huxley!

1361
01:36:50.372 --> 01:36:51.415
Chief...

1362
01:36:51.498 --> 01:36:54.868
...you can take this job
and you can shovel it. Hmm?

1363
01:36:57.212 --> 01:36:58.881
"Take this job...

1364
01:36:59.089 --> 01:37:00.933
"...and shovel it."
- Yeah?

1365
01:37:02.260 --> 01:37:03.761
Close enough.

1366
01:37:09.184 --> 01:37:13.522
I hadn't counted on this but I must say,
you worked out beautifully.

1367
01:37:14.607 --> 01:37:16.525
People are terrified of you.

1368
01:37:16.859 --> 01:37:19.695
What's new? People have always been
terrified of me.

1369
01:37:19.779 --> 01:37:22.656
Yes, but this time they're really intimidated.

1370
01:37:24.910 --> 01:37:26.119
Now...

1371
01:37:26.411 --> 01:37:30.165
...I'll have carte blanche
to create the perfect society.

1372
01:37:31.833 --> 01:37:33.251
My society.

1373
01:37:34.169 --> 01:37:37.048
San Angeles will be a beacon of order...

1374
01:37:37.840 --> 01:37:40.468
...with the purity of an ant colony.

1375
01:37:41.302 --> 01:37:43.888
And the beauty of a flawless pearl.

1376
01:37:44.322 --> 01:37:46.891
Look, you can't take away people's right to be assholes.

1377
01:37:49.353 --> 01:37:50.854
That's who you remind me of...

1378
01:37:51.605 --> 01:37:53.232
...an evil Mr. Rogers.

1379
01:37:53.440 --> 01:37:55.025
Will you please kill him?

1380
01:37:55.108 --> 01:37:56.652
He's pissing me off.

1381
01:38:07.330 --> 01:38:09.499
Put another log on the fire!

1382
01:38:11.084 --> 01:38:13.212
I'll love running this place!

1383
01:38:20.469 --> 01:38:21.929
Well, now...

1384
01:38:22.221 --> 01:38:25.273
...what shall I do with you. Huh, Bobby?

1385
01:38:26.184 --> 01:38:28.687
I am an excellent associate, sir.

1386
01:38:29.271 --> 01:38:33.233
I'd be delighted to continue my services
during your administration.

1387
01:38:33.601 --> 01:38:35.735
Huh, Danzig, maybe we'll use him--

1388
01:38:35.819 --> 01:38:37.864
Excuse me, the police are here.

1389
01:38:39.115 --> 01:38:40.408
Oh, man!

1390
01:39:06.436 --> 01:39:08.521
Where the fuck do you think... Ow!

1391
01:39:26.624 --> 01:39:28.001
I'm impressed.

1392
01:39:41.557 --> 01:39:43.893
That man has died by my hands.

1393
01:39:44.602 --> 01:39:46.312
It was either him or us, Huxley.

1394
01:39:47.772 --> 01:39:49.273
Yeah, there is that.

1395
01:39:49.482 --> 01:39:51.734
Anyway, where the hell did you learn to kick like that?

1396
01:39:52.986 --> 01:39:54.780
Jackie Chan movies.

1397
01:40:03.247 --> 01:40:06.209
Looks like the Cocteau plan
just went up in smoke.

1398
01:40:06.668 --> 01:40:09.045
Rest in peace, Raymond Cocteau.

1399
01:40:10.046 --> 01:40:14.008
Oh, John Spartan, civilization as we know it
will come to an end.

1400
01:40:15.051 --> 01:40:16.177
What will we do?

1401
01:40:16.261 --> 01:40:18.848
I don't know, but trust me, this is better for you.

1402
01:40:19.014 --> 01:40:20.474
What's that?

1403
01:40:25.354 --> 01:40:26.814
Oh, this is bad.

1404
01:40:27.106 --> 01:40:28.357
This is very bad.

1405
01:40:28.440 --> 01:40:32.445
He's accessed the cryo-prison
and is about to defrost the entire multi-lifer wing.

1406
01:40:32.571 --> 01:40:34.072
Most of them don't like you.

1407
01:40:34.239 --> 01:40:37.742
Most of these guys don't even like
their own mothers. They're bad boys, Huxley.

1408
01:40:37.826 --> 01:40:39.286
How many are there?

1409
01:40:42.498 --> 01:40:43.499
Eighty.

1410
01:40:43.791 --> 01:40:45.209
All without rehab.

1411
01:40:45.293 --> 01:40:47.253
They'll be re-animated within the hour.

1412
01:40:47.336 --> 01:40:49.088
Oh, we gotta stop this.

1413
01:40:50.965 --> 01:40:55.387
I'm not at all pleased about having caused
the fatality of that deranged cryo-convict.

1414
01:40:55.637 --> 01:40:59.850
I now understand that under certain
circumstances that violence is necessary.

1415
01:41:00.058 --> 01:41:01.226
Good.

1416
01:41:05.940 --> 01:41:08.109
I hope you understand this.

1417
01:41:17.076 --> 01:41:19.413
I hope my butt didn't look like that.

1418
01:41:19.580 --> 01:41:22.333
Okay, who do we have left that's good, huh?

1419
01:41:22.500 --> 01:41:23.667
Let's see...

1420
01:41:23.793 --> 01:41:25.294
...Foulks, Patrick.

1421
01:41:25.461 --> 01:41:27.963
Jeffrey Dahmer? I love that guy.

1422
01:41:28.048 --> 01:41:30.759
Look, we gotta get him.
How long before the rest are done?

1423
01:41:30.842 --> 01:41:32.844
They're in the final stages of reanimation, sir.

1424
01:41:32.928 --> 01:41:34.763
Great. Absolutely great.

1425
01:41:36.556 --> 01:41:37.682
Gentlemen!

1426
01:41:38.225 --> 01:41:41.686
Thank you very much, but your services
will no longer be required.

1427
01:41:48.778 --> 01:41:51.197
Send a maniac to catch a maniac.

1428
01:42:09.384 --> 01:42:10.718
"Attention"

1429
01:42:10.885 --> 01:42:12.262
"Attention"

1430
01:42:12.345 --> 01:42:15.140
"Cryo-prisoner defrosting
re-animation sequence..."

1431
01:42:15.223 --> 01:42:17.475
"...now entering final stage"

1432
01:42:19.394 --> 01:42:22.523
"Countdown to reanimation
of prisoner batches..."

1433
01:42:22.731 --> 01:42:26.525
"...290, 310, 480..."

1434
01:42:26.819 --> 01:42:28.070
"...and 570"

1435
01:42:28.404 --> 01:42:29.822
"Ten minutes"

1436
01:42:31.907 --> 01:42:34.578
- That's it. The very last one.
- Excellent.

1437
01:42:36.037 --> 01:42:37.372
"Accessed"

1438
01:42:39.082 --> 01:42:40.834
What the hell is that?

1439
01:43:17.415 --> 01:43:19.542
Didn't expect that one, did you?

1440
01:43:19.918 --> 01:43:21.336
Where the fuck you going?

1441
01:43:21.419 --> 01:43:23.339
I wish you the best of luck, sir.

1442
01:43:24.340 --> 01:43:25.341
Stupid.

1443
01:43:32.757 --> 01:43:34.768
Spartan, how's it hanging, huh?

1444
01:43:36.353 --> 01:43:39.481
I'm sure you're familiar
with the long arm of the law.

1445
01:43:44.486 --> 01:43:47.573
Oh, come on Spartan, won't you struggle a little bit?
Make me work for it, huh?

1446
01:43:47.657 --> 01:43:49.534
What do you say? How about...

1447
01:43:49.617 --> 01:43:52.703
...a little target practice. What do you say?

1448
01:44:00.921 --> 01:44:02.631
Oops, didn't hurt your head?

1449
01:44:22.944 --> 01:44:24.530
Shit! Goddamn!

1450
01:44:32.121 --> 01:44:33.038
Fuck!

1451
01:44:45.135 --> 01:44:46.511
That's it, Spartan!

1452
01:44:47.053 --> 01:44:49.265
You're not getting out of this one!

1453
01:44:52.268 --> 01:44:54.896
I could drop you in that vat of defrost, over there...

1454
01:44:55.062 --> 01:44:57.148
...and fry your ass like a chicken...

1455
01:44:58.357 --> 01:45:01.445
...or with my little pinky,
drop your monkey ass down--

1456
01:45:04.072 --> 01:45:05.657
I'll be goddamned.

1457
01:45:47.035 --> 01:45:48.328
Shit! Goddamn!

1458
01:45:48.578 --> 01:45:49.580
What am I doing wrong?

1459
01:45:49.789 --> 01:45:51.624
"Cryo-prisoner re-animation..."

1460
01:45:51.749 --> 01:45:54.460
"...sequence now entering final stage"

1461
01:46:01.133 --> 01:46:03.846
"Is it cold in here, or is it just me?"

1462
01:46:05.556 --> 01:46:07.015
Good memory.

1463
01:46:13.355 --> 01:46:14.649
Come here!

1464
01:46:15.066 --> 01:46:16.234
Shit!

1465
01:46:27.079 --> 01:46:28.539
I hate cops!

1466
01:46:32.877 --> 01:46:35.462
Look into my eyes, John. I'll see you in hell.

1467
01:46:35.880 --> 01:46:36.839
Not.

1468
01:47:20.053 --> 01:47:22.472
This is the best day of my life.

1469
01:47:52.922 --> 01:47:54.257
Heads up!

1470
01:48:45.228 --> 01:48:49.149
You've apprehended the villain responsible
for murdering our beloved Dr. Raymond Cocteau?

1471
01:48:49.357 --> 01:48:51.234
Well, I wouldn't exactly say "apprehend".

1472
01:48:51.401 --> 01:48:52.903
Let's just say he's history.

1473
01:48:53.153 --> 01:48:54.780
And the cryo-prison...

1474
01:48:54.906 --> 01:48:56.365
...that's history, too.

1475
01:48:59.327 --> 01:49:00.870
What'll we do?

1476
01:49:01.829 --> 01:49:02.955
How will we live?

1477
01:49:03.039 --> 01:49:06.793
I'll tell you what we're gonna do. We'll go out drinking,
all of us, get shit-faced and paint the town, literally.

1478
01:49:07.085 --> 01:49:08.996
Put up graffiti, slogans, it'll be a blast.

1479
01:49:08.997 --> 01:49:09.795
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

1480
01:49:09.796 --> 01:49:11.256
I'm gonna tell you what you're gonna do.

1481
01:49:11.340 --> 01:49:13.258
Why don't you get a little dirty...

1482
01:49:13.342 --> 01:49:15.093
...you, a lot clean.

1483
01:49:15.302 --> 01:49:17.429
And somewhere in the middle....

1484
01:49:18.222 --> 01:49:20.099
I don't know, you'll figure it out.

1485
01:49:20.433 --> 01:49:21.643
Fucking-A!

1486
01:49:24.812 --> 01:49:25.705
Well put.

1487
01:49:25.706 --> 01:49:27.406
Mister Friendly. Mister Friendly?

1488
01:49:27.690 --> 01:49:29.817
Greetings and salutations, Edgar Friendly.

1489
01:49:29.984 --> 01:49:32.363
I'm Associate Bob. And may I say...

1490
01:49:32.530 --> 01:49:35.950
...it'll be a great pleasure
to assist you creating a more humane--

1491
01:49:35.951 --> 01:49:36.951
Bob, Bob.

1492
01:49:37.201 --> 01:49:38.953
- Let's talk about the hair, okay?
- Hair?

1493
01:49:39.036 --> 01:49:42.748
- Pick a color, right? And lose the kimono. You look like a couch.
- Couch?

1494
01:49:42.873 --> 01:49:45.418
What are you, a surgeon with these gloves?

1495
01:49:49.422 --> 01:49:52.050
Thank you for rendering me unconscious.

1496
01:49:54.052 --> 01:49:55.512
Huxley, I did it for your own good.

1497
01:49:55.595 --> 01:49:57.932
- We're supposed to be a team.
- We are.

